/*
 * Midi "Turing Machine" Sequence Generator
 * 
 * 
 * Controls:
 * <mode>   x       PLAY      CHNL      THRU     PC       CT       PCT
 *    
 *    POT  mutate   sc.var     key      divn     tie%     len      chnl
 *         
 *  t [o]  BPM                            -
 *  c [o]  #octs    st.oct      -
 *    
 *  p [o]  sc.fam      -
 *    
 */


